name: RTCInboundRtpStreamStats
description: The WebRTC API's RTCInboundRtpStreamStats dictionary, based upon RTCReceivedRtpStreamStats and RTCStats, contains statistics related to the receiving end of an RTP stream on the local end of the RTCPeerConnection.
